The British are leaving! The British are leaving!
(Don't worry, they'll be back soon.) 

Absinthe's resident Limeys, The Desk Jockeys (@desk.jockeys) and Matt and Valentina (@mattandvaliskateduo), are hopping the pond to perform at the @f1 British Grand Prix this Sunday!

The Gazillionaire had this to say: “Before this invitation arrived, I didn’t know much about Formula 1, but now I am thinking of entering my Rolls Royce in the Las Vegas race in November. It has many more cylinders and is way more comfortable than what the drivers here are getting around in."
